
extends help

block prepend variables
  - var pageID = 'help-commands'
  - var pageHeading = 'List of Commands'

block content
  div
    p To improve the browsing efficiency, we have provided a command-line interface. The commands serve as shortcuts and can be used in the 
      code.ui-color-emphasis terminal
      |  page or the 
      strong "Search or type a command"
      |  box.
    ul
      each entry in commands
        li
          strong= entry.command
          |  &mdash; #{entry.description}
          div
            span Usage: 
            code.ui-color-emphasis= entry.usage
          div
            span Options: 
            ul.ui-list-unstyled.ui-offset-large
              each item in entry.options
                li
                  code.ui-color-emphasis= item.option
                  span.ui-offset-large!= item.description
